HEADWORD: Diallel
<hw>Di"al*lel</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/
crossing.]</ety> <def>Meeting and intersecting, as lines; not parallel;
-- opposed to <contr>parallel</contr>.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
